  "text": "The higher-order nature of the 'group by' and windowing operators in our streaming algebra resembles the \"Apply\" operator that is used inside Microsoft SQL Server and has been discussed by Galindo-Legaria et al. [CITATION_1] . Similar rewrite rules as the ones in SQL Server may also help the Glacier compiler to improve the quality of generated plans.",
